    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marcel van Kervinck</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/kervinck\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/4e/MarcelvanKervinck.jpg/240px-MarcelvanKervinck.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/4/4e/MarcelvanKervinck.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MarcelvanKervinck.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Marcel van Kervinck <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Marcel van Kervinck</b>, (March 27, 1972 – May 25, 2020 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>)<br />\nwas a Dutch software engineer and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metrology\">metrology</a>. Marcel was author of the chess programs <a href=\"/Rookie\" title=\"Rookie\">Rookie</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, <a href=\"/MSCP\" title=\"MSCP\">MSCP</a> (Marcel’s Simple Chess Program) <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, and the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> engine <a href=\"/Floyd\" title=\"Floyd\">Floyd</a> for study purposes <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>, author of the online <a href=\"/Opening\" title=\"Opening\">opening</a> database <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bookie&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bookie (page does not exist)\">Bookie</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>, and co-author of the <a href=\"/Hardware#Gigatron\" title=\"Hardware\">Gigatron</a> retro-style 8-bit microcomputer <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>. From December 2012 until November 2014, he was a member of the board of the <a href=\"/CSVN\" title=\"CSVN\">CSVN</a>. \nMarcel van Kervinck passed away on May 25, 2020 <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1994_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1994 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.csvn.nl/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=487%3A30th-odccc-final-results&amp;catid=51%3Atoernooien&amp;Itemid=28&amp;lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"MarcelPPrize.jpg\" src=\"/images/6/62/MarcelPPrize.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p>Marcel van Kervinck receives the Programmer's Prize <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> by <a href=\"/CSVN\" title=\"CSVN\">CSVN</a> chairman <a href=\"/Cock_de_Gorter\" title=\"Cock de Gorter\">Cock de Gorter</a>, <a href=\"/DOCCC_2010\" title=\"DOCCC 2010\">DOCCC 2010</a> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>The design and implementation of the Rookie 2.0 Chess Playing Program</i>. Masters Thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://alexandria.tue.nl/extra2/afstversl/wsk-i/kervinck2002.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://marcelk.net/thesis/talk-eval-rookie/sld001.htm\">A pattern-recognition strategy for chess position evaluation</a></i>. Slides from <i>The design and implementation of the Rookie 2.0 Chess Playing Program</i>.</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>A fast software-based method for upcoming cycle detection in search trees</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://marcelk.net/2013-04-06/paper/upcoming-rep-v2.pdf\">pdf preview</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1994_...\">1994 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1994 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess/KnJvBnhgDKU/yCi5yBx18PQJ\">Tricky bit tricks</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rec.games.chess</a>, October 20, 1994&#160;» <a href=\"/Traversing_Subsets_of_a_Set\" title=\"Traversing Subsets of a Set\">Traversing Subsets of a Set</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38997\">Inverse delta pruning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 06, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=410664&amp;t=39407\">Re: Programmers: what's the story behind the name of your engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40166\">Ahhh... the holy grail of computer chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 23, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2300\">Upcoming repetition detection</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, April 06, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=2336\">ICT13 programmer's report: Rookie v3.7</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, June 04, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/ICT_2013\" title=\"ICT 2013\">ICT 2013</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55224\">Some SMP measurements with Rookie v3</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Rookie\" title=\"Rookie\">Rookie</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=30107\">Grafty vs Crafty</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, April 21, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57482\">Name for elo without draws?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57517\">Yet another KPK endgame table generator: pfkpk</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 05, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/KPK\" title=\"KPK\">KPK</a>, <a href=\"/Endgame_Bitbases\" title=\"Endgame Bitbases\">Endgame Bitbases</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57913\">Floyd 0.5 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Oct 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Floyd\" title=\"Floyd\">Floyd</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://marcelk.net/\">Marcel's web pages</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kervinck/\">Marcel van Kervinck | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kervinck\">kervinck (Marcel van Kervinck) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=798\">Marcel van Kervinck's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hackaday.io/project/20781-8-bit-color-computer-from-ttl\">8-bit color computer from TTL</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcel van Kervinck</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hackaday\">Hackaday.io</a>, 2017 <sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup> </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcel_van_Kervinck&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kervinck\">kervinck (Marcel van Kervinck) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofo